headline: PainTEQ Scales Leadership: Med-Tech Catalyst Robert Kline Joins Board to Drive New Standard in Interventional Spine Care
summary: Med-tech veteran Robert Kline has joined the Board of Directors at PainTEQ, a strategic move to capitalize on his commercialization and growth expertise as the company redefines interventional spine care.
